('97121','33517','5','Modern newly built villa in Nova St. Ponsa for sale'),
('97122','33518','5','The modern villa stands on a 945m² plot with partial sea views in Nova Santa Ponsa in south west Mallorca. In the immediate vicinity are several golf courses, marinas and a well built infrastructure. The villa was built in 2014-2015 with quality materials created such as Schüko aluminum double glazed sliding windows, electr. security shutters, self-supporting stairs, Alno laser kitchen with Neff appliances incl. Steamer, floor heating and hot water via heat pump (Stiebel Eltron), Security aluminum outer ect doors with fingerprint system, Loxone BUS technology, outdoor swimming pool (salt electrolysis). The ground floor has a spacious entrance hall, bright living room with high ceiling and gallery, modern kitchen, utility room and a guest bedroom and a guest toilet with shower. On the 1st floor there is a gallery, a master bedroom with dressing room, bathroom and terrace and a bedroom with dressing room and bathroom en suite. The garage in the basement (112m²) can accommodate 3-4 cars.'),
